<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-2">Accommodation</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Access to TV<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Internet access<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Public telephone<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="no">Family accommodation<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Mobile phones permitted<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="no">Private rooms only<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Single sex accommodation only<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent6e2956ef07184a62a733f7f8ad93ce6a">
</div>
<p>Mobile phones are permitted with provisos; details can be found in our Handbook for Inpatients. <br/><br/><strong>For information about our facilities please click on the link below:</strong></p>
<p><a href="http://www.royalpapworth.nhs.uk/content.php?/about/facts_figures" target="_blank">Papworth Hospital Facilities</a></p>
<p><strong>Vistors Accommodation</strong></p>
<p>Information on local<br/>accommodation is available<br/>from the Accommodation<br/>Officer - on 01480 364958 or<br/>by emailing: <br/><a href="mailto:papworth.accommodation@nhs.net">papworth.accommodation@nhs.net</a></p>
<p>A list of premises can also be viewed<br/>on our <a href="http://www.royalpapworth.nhs.uk/content.php?/patients_visitors/patient_information/accommodation_for_patients_and_patient_relatives" target="_blank">website</a></p>
<p> </p>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
