<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-3">Bringing children to Royal Papworth Hospital</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="no">Baby changing facility<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="no">Children's play area<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="no">Parent and child parking<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="no">Parent and baby room<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="no">Pram park<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent8bf0aafa8a3c46c6a6e3ce8d151e44a9">
</div>
<p>Please check in advance with the nurse in charge of the appropriate ward whether children under the age of two years are allowed to visit the patient.</p>
<p>Please note that the pond is deep and the swan is sometimes aggressive.</p>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-4">Counselling and Support</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Bereavement support<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Translation services<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent4382edda2bb94ba99a7233f8bd654e14">
</div>
<p>Whilst Papworth Hospital does not have a dedicated counselling service, we are able to speak with patients, families and carers on an individual basis and signpost them to specific counselling services to best meet their needs.  We also have a social worker on site for those patients coming from outside of Cambridgeshire and can provide contact information about this service through the PALS office or the Social Work Department on 1480 364279, or 01480 364361.</p>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-5">Faith services</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Prayer area<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">On-site chapel<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent6964f28342944a6bbecf58e0cfe7938a">
</div>
<p><a href="http://www.royalpapworth.nhs.uk/content.php?/patients_visitors/patient_information/during_your_stay_in_hospital" target="_blank">The Chaplaincy Service</a> - Pastoral and Spiritual Care</p>
<p>The hospital employs a whole-time Chaplain, who is supported by a local Roman Catholic Priest, and by a Chaplaincy Assistant and a small team of Chaplaincy volunteers. They visit all the wards regularly and have local contacts for all the major faiths and denominations.</p>
<p>Please contact the Chaplaincy Service on 01480 364121 if you have any queries or special requirements or would like further information.</p>
</div>
<div class="col two-sm last">
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="panel">
<div class="panel-content">
<div class="pad clear">
<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-6">Food and amenities on-site</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Cafe<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="no">Patient library<span class="hidden"> (no)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Pharmacy<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Shop<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent27c858eb4c514840836a8fe5b941a095">
</div>
<p>The Garden Restaurant</p>
<p>Patients and vistors are welcome to use the restauarant which is open from 0730 to 1900 seven days a week. </p>
<ul>
<li>Breakfast is served from 0730 to 0900</li>
<li>Lunch is served from 1200 to 1400</li>
<li>Supper is served from 1730 to 1900</li>
</ul>
</div>
