<div class="col clear facility">
<div class="col three-sm">
<h3 id="FacilityGroupProxy38812ac03cfb4f2ba06c302e810ef43e-7">Parking</h3>
<ul class="facility-list clear">
<li class="yes">Car Parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Cycle parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
<li class="yes">Disabled parking<span class="hidden"> (yes)</span></li>
</ul>
<div id="imageContent7427d07692a5422b91549b99fc86ca6e">
</div>
<p><strong><a href="http://www.royalpapworth.nhs.uk/content.php?/home/how_to_find_us" target="_blank">Getting Here</a></strong></p>
<p><strong>Car parking charges </strong>are in<br/>place at Papworth Hospital. All<br/>patients and visitors parking<br/>on the site need to display<br/>a parking ticket or appropriate<br/>permit. Signs around the<br/>hospital will show you where<br/>patients and visitors may park<br/>‘pay and display’. Charges<br/>apply from 0700 to 2000<br/>every day.</p>
<p><strong>Current Charges</strong></p>
<p>Up to 3 hours             £2.50</p>
<p>3-5 hours                    £3.00</p>
<p>Full day                        £5.00</p>
<p>Weekly ticket               £10.00</p>
<p>Monthly ticket              £20.00</p>
</div>
